17 Yunlin Street.
云林街十七号。
17 Yunlin Street.
这场战役 我们与你们同在。
We are with you in this battle.
正是千千万万“无言者”的声音，才给了我们，认识时代真相的可能。
It is the thousands of "speechless" voices that give us the possibility of knowing the truth of the times.
Play以上视频资料来自“云林街十七号”受访者感谢他们的发声从1月23日宣布武汉封城开始，中国人便注定要度过一个难忘的新年。
2007-9-25 21: 48 Chinese people are destined to have an unforgettable New Year ever since the announcement of Wuhan on January 23, 2007.
在愤怒，悲伤，感动和各种各样的情绪交织下，确诊人数终于在8万止步。
With anger, sadness, emotion and all sorts of emotions interwoven, the number of people diagnosed finally stopped at 80, 000.
随着各地陆续复工，暂停键上的手指似乎快要移开。
As work resumes everywhere, the fingers on the pause key seem to be moving.
但我们都知道，即将开始的，已经不是我们曾经离开的地方。
But we all know that what is about to begin is not where we left off.
也是从武汉封城开始，“云林街十七号”开始向外界广泛征集“#普通人的抗疫生活#”。
Also from Wuhan sealing city, "17 Yunlin Street" began to collect from the outside world "# ordinary people's life against the disease #."
截止到目前，我们收回了一百多份由受访者认真作答的采访视频。
So far, we have collected more than 100 video interviews to which the respondents have given serious replies.
这里面有在武汉城内坚守的居民，也有国内外热心的志愿者，更多的，是暂停键按下后一些无所适从的普通人。
This includes the city of Wuhan adhere to the residents, but also at home and abroad enthusiastic volunteers, more, is to pause the key to press some of the ordinary people at a loss.
而我们的采访问题，也总和疫情期间大家最关心的问题相关。
And our interview questions are also related to the issues that people are most concerned about during the epidemic.
这是我们2月中旬的一份提纲。
Here is an outline for us in mid-February.
为了对抗遗忘，共同守住这份记忆，“云林街十七号”推出“无言者声”视频系列。
To fight oblivion, jointly hold this memory, "17 Yunlin Street" launched "mute voice" video series.
在这个同“404”对抗的时代，这里可能没有撕心裂肺的故事，但却有或冷静或激烈的思考。
In this era of confrontation with 404, there may be no heart-rending story here, but there is either calm or intense thinking.
你不会流泪，但会感到无比熟悉。
You won't cry, but you'll feel very familiar.
第一期视频我们选择了#隔离在家的日子#这个主题，是希望在复工之后，大家还能记起疫情曾带给我们的影响，也是为了保证第一期视频能够顺利发出。
In the first video we chose the # Isolated Home Day # theme, in the hope that after returning to work, you will remember the impact of the epidemic on us, and to ensure that the first video can be sent smoothly.
正是千千万万“无言者”的声音，才给了我们，认识时代真相的可能。
It is the thousands of "speechless" voices that give us the possibility of knowing the truth of the times.
“无言者声”系列每周六更新一期下期预告“我和我散落在武汉的朋友”#海外视频征集#——你回国了吗？“云林街十七号”是一个独立纪录片团队。
The mute voice series is updated every Saturday with the next issue of "I and my friends scattered in Wuhan" # Overseas video collection # - Have you returned home? "Seventeen Yunlin Street" is an independent documentary team.
新冠疫情爆发至今，我们除了在武汉进行了深入的拍摄，也在广泛征集外围视频，邀请大家和我们一起参与这次记录新冠疫情的创作。
So far, in addition to the outbreak of the new crown in Wuhan, we have conducted in-depth shooting, but also in the collection of a wide range of peripheral video, we invite you to join us in this record of the new crown epidemic.
随着国际疫情的爆发，越来越多的人被卷入这次“大流行”。
With the outbreak of international epidemic, more and more people are involved in this "pandemic."
很多在外华人，选择回到国内。
Many overseas Chinese have chosen to return home.
为了更好地记录，我们想要邀请你回答几个简单的问题，条件允许的情况下，尽可能多的拍摄一些回程的视频。
For a better record, we would like to invite you to answer a few simple questions and, if conditions permit, take as many videos as possible for the return trip.
拍摄要求1.尽量横屏拍摄。
Photo requirements 1. Try to shoot across the screen.
2.保证光线充足。
2. Make sure the light is adequate.
3.尽量选择高画质。
3. Try to choose high quality pictures.
参考问题 所在地的疫情如何？为什么选择回国？同行的有哪些人？ 家人是否支持你们回国的决定？ 为了回国做了哪些准备？遇到了哪些困难？ 当地人如何看待你们回国的行为？ 回国路上有什么印象深刻的事？回国后，是否隔离？隔离的状态如何？需要画面记录自己觉得有意思的瞬间1. 采访视频：回答以上的问题2. 回国的防护物资采办，行李整理3.回国前和房东、朋友告别4. 从家去往机场路上，搭乘各种交通工具的视频5. 抵达机场后，机场、安检（防疫检测）和候机室的视频6. 回国后，机场、安检（防疫检测）的视频7. 隔离点和隔离日常联系我们158276081981507143168215189681188（电话和微信同号）微博：云林街十七号b站：云林街十七号● 联系我们让我们听到你的声音。
What is the epidemic situation in the area where the problem is located? Why did you choose to return home? Who did you go with? What did your family do to support you? What did you do to return home?
